posting_body: ['Close to Everything!', "Conveniently located boutique charm in Belltown's historic", 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 82', 'OR Text', '82', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'The Goodwin', '2233 1st', 'Ave, Seattle, WA, 98121', 'Interested In This Unit?', 'Use this link for more details:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1.5 Bath, approximately 1282 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'The 34 homes of the Goodwin rest on one of Seattle’s most storied intersections at First and Bell.', 'Originally a part of Louis Rowe’s strip of storefronts, 2233 First has been known throughout the city’s exciting history as the National Sheet Metal Company, Hotel Grace, and many other monikers and embodiments.', 'It is apropos that this prolific and historic corner continues its likeness as a place that’s centrally located, attainable for everyone, and undeniably Seattle.', 'Features', '- Kitchen with High-End Appliances & Gas Stove', '- Refrigerator', '- Dishwasher', '- Air Conditioning', '- Heat', '- Hardwood Floors', '- Washer/Dryer', '- Balcony', '- Granite Countertops', '- Alarm System', '- Cable/Satellite', 'Community Amenities', '- The Lobby', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- Online Payments Available', '- Fetch Package Delivery', '- Spacious library with books, magazines, and local papers', '- Iconic views of the city', '- Rooftop with a grilling station, lounge area, garden and firepits', 'Pet Policy', 'Max 2 pets per apartment', 'Income Requirements:', '3x rent', '5x rent (guarantor)', 'Office Hours', 'Tuesday-Saturday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'PAZqvAO7RO']
